5. Flutter/Dart Dependencies

The following Flutter/Dart components are used in the frontend application:

- Flutter SDK (BSD-3-Clause) - https://flutter.dev
- drift (MIT) - Database ORM for Flutter
- sqlcipher_flutter_libs (MIT option chosen) - Native SQLCipher encryption
- flutter_riverpod (MIT) - State management
- sodium (BSD-3-Clause) - libsodium cryptography bindings
- flutter_inappwebview (Apache-2.0) - WebView for 3D avatar rendering
- dio (MIT) - HTTP client
- go_router (BSD-3-Clause) - Navigation
- And other MIT/BSD-3-Clause licensed packages

For complete Flutter dependency list:
  cd frontend && flutter pub deps --style=list

================================================================================

For a complete list of all Python dependencies and their licenses, run:
  uv run pip-licenses --format=markdown --with-urls

For Flutter dependencies:
  cd frontend && flutter pub deps --style=list

